Title: AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF BUCAOBUCAO, MUNICIPALITY OF DAO, PROVINCE OF ANTIQUE, TO THAT OF YSULAT.
Data:
[ Commonwealth Act No. 582, June 08, 1940 ]
AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF BUCAOBUCAO, MUNICIPALITY OF DAO, PROVINCE OF ANTIQUE, TO THAT OF YSULAT.
Be it enacted by the National Assembly of the Philippines:
Section 1. The name of the barrio of Bucaobucao of the Municipality of Dao, Province of Antique, is changed to that of Ysulat.ℒαwρhi৷
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Enacted, without Executive approval, June 8, 1940.
